Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:21.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身披天馬聖衣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.91,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔天際
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:27.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:31.64,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無遲疑的雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泛著淚光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:38.02,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不含一絲陰翳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱使遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:43.13,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱使身死戰地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:47.52,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了跨越那障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:50.12,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們堅定不移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:51.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如星辰般閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:53.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星座起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:55.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:57.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作指引勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:00.58,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:03.40,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那有限的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒不息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:07.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們至深的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現明晰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未知的極限的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:14.22,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友情編織成的神話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:15.52,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:16.51,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:19.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮字幕組&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的時光毀滅奪走了他的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就失去了一個所謂的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的小宇宙不過是Ω的皮毛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是贏不了我許珀裡翁的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是為了監視昴才來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻救不了昴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒吧！究極的Ω！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 我已經死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過時間停止了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間停止？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 昴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凌駕人類的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都想不起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那即是說 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機尚未成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:04:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情你似乎知道些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的話 就告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有過去的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要回到同伴們的身邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人很快就會駕臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 礙事的就全部收拾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道昴是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那個小鬼 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然值得讓你再次站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了看清昴的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:05:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一有變 就親手將其葬送
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你應該感謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了我們而捨身戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這次輪到我來戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了昴 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說為了同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我現身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感覺到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人類世界與人類接觸讓你學到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學到了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話說得太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好奇怪的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說自己是凌駕於人類之上的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:06:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此 你卻一點都不明白人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 讓我告訴你吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類可是強大得一塌糊塗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類只要集結起了同伴 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有什麼懼怕的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可以凌駕於神之上哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別犯蠢了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渺小脆弱的人類怎麼可能凌駕於神明之上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的體內明明流著神之血 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要期望的話 甚至可以成為神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而你卻為了那個小子 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了人類而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想要作為一個人類生存下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類遠比神明要來得高潔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論面對怎樣的苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會直面困難 堅持在自己的道路上走下去 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會停下前進的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一次又一次跌倒 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定會爬起來 繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份堅韌的力量 甚至可以凌駕於神力之上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是人類真正的強大之處！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你所說的人類的強大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是讓我吃驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區青銅居然三番五次地成群向我攻來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子我被小看了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不管多少次都會站起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就像昴那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像昴那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像昴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像昴那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像昴那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴們的聲音傳達到了我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什麼都沒聽到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在為我而戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能就這樣呆著 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去他們那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能從這裡出去的只有力量勝過許珀裡翁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要有神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那樣正好 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是終將成為神的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這種事現在怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我必須要去同伴們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不知道我的身份 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻依舊信任著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有信任著我的同伴在 我就要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在 我必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任之心化作了光之路標 指引了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回到那些信任並接納了我的夥伴們的身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青銅們想要釋放出最後的光輝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等渺小的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們夠了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我就此終結你們聖鬥士的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩滅震擊（Shock of Destruction）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了聖衣 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就連向我揮拳也做不到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遺憾了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所相信的那些人類同伴看來已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們才不會死呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子你是被人類感化的有些過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們才不會死呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.88,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒吧！究極的Ω！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們死掉什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類都背負著死亡的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事的人就全部消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就只剩下那位大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在與同伴並肩戰鬥時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在於人心中的 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關懷他人 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為他人而戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是深藏於我們心中的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒會讓我們的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我們守護同伴的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴湧而出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予我們全新的風 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煥然一新的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予我們奮力而起 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重現利齒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失去了聖衣也要向我抗爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴那傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然總叫囂著要成為神 要打倒我什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡說些孩子氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他竟然能如此打動大家的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個了不得的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連神都能擊敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類所擁有的最強力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要憑借這種力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救昴！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢話連篇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西怎麼可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我這就證明給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡根本就是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我們人類而言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡是存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經受了那樣的挫折與傷害 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙卻燃燒得愈發高昂 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會存在這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這只不過是幻覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不存在的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那將其抹消便可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用我的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切歸零吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了昴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了昴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了昴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到昴君回來為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了昴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟鳴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展翅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴湧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘶吼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還能站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奇跡的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其化作可能的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在為了我而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓你的存在 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一切都灰飛煙滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時光災變（Chrono Catastrophe）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然憑肉身就擋住了我的拳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小宇宙的光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中創造了宇宙的大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是處於它的前階段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙暴漲 Inflation！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是創造宇宙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大宇宙（Macrocosmo） 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感覺到 大宇宙的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙在共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同星辰間的引力一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此吸引
