Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光牙他們的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒是Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道發生了奇跡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要趕緊過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往夥伴們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們終於覺醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 這就是Ω？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們覺醒了真正的Ω力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就算拼上我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要把他們打倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那位大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩滅震擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Ω的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我啊 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你現在的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能逃離這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
