Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然要為了那位大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻出我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們同歸於盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能打碎這件刻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人一定能成功復活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給人類世界帶來終結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我拼上性命戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是人類的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你不是看到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類能引發奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份力量對人類來說過於沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神才能擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總有一天 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求戰鬥的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的靈魂被女神所指引
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士中以魯莽著稱的哈賓格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如猛牛一般的戰士 根本不知愛與正義為何物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對聖鬥士的驕傲毫不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將命運交付於他的女神的真意究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
